er to the next level!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178990/extras/9f92e873f656308692134101aa0a2ac3.poster.avif?t=1773317119\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178990/extras/9f92e873f656308692134101aa0a2ac3.webm?t=1773317119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178990/extras/9f92e873f656308692134101aa0a2ac3.mp4?t=1773317119\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >    Explore Your Spaceship</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Relax between runs in your spaceship, meet new characters and explore more of the Sodaman universe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178990/extras/27f2ec79fb64e967aa2970b149f65d2d.poster.avif?t=1773317119\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178990/extras/27f2ec79fb64e967aa2970b149f65d2d.webm?t=1773317119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178990/extras/27f2ec79fb64e967aa2970b149f65d2d.mp4?t=1773317119\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178990/extras/e9c8ef949c21e7555181f4bde69f77a4.poster.avif?t=1773317119\" width=600 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/21789